Example workflow — callback registration with user data:
```c
typedef void (*EventCallback)(int eventCode, void *userData);

typedef struct EventSource
{
    EventCallback callback;
    void *userData;
} EventSource;

void EventSource_Notify(EventSource *source, int code)
{
    if (source->callback) source->callback(code, source->userData);
}
```

