Encode a big-endian 16-bit value explicitly.

Example workflow — big-endian frame encode/decode helpers:
```c
#include <stdint.h>
#include <stddef.h>

static uint16_t ReadBe16(const uint8_t *buffer)
{
    return (uint16_t)(((uint16_t)buffer[0] << 8) |
                      ((uint16_t)buffer[1]));
}

static void WriteBe16(uint8_t *buffer, uint16_t value)
{
    buffer[0] = (uint8_t)(value >> 8);
    buffer[1] = (uint8_t)(value & 0xFFu);
}
```

